table_definition:
SELECT  CONCAT(prefisso_matricola, matricola) as matricola_estesa,
        CAST(matricola AS INT) AS matricola,
        cognome, 
        nome, 
        data_nascita,
        codice_fiscale, 
        '' AS sesso, 
        cast(null as int) as codice_cittadino,
        'rce' AS provenienza
FROM (
    SELECT  *,
            8 as codice_ente
    FROM    fbk_test1__CORE_DATASET.RCE_ANAGRAFICA) t1
LEFT JOIN   fbk_test1__MASTER_DATA.MAPPING_ENTE t2 ON t1.codice_ente = t2.codice_ente
